Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:26.27,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,210)}I wake once again to a sleepy morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:32.90,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,210)}And carefully fasten my necktie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:39.37,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,210)}As I pass the door to the classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:46.25,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,0)}I walk with my chest held just a little high
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:53.38,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,120)}The wind blows through the days spent just like this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:56.84,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I heard it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:01:02.85,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I felt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:06.73,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,It now trembles within my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:10.11,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,190)}I felt it would happen soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:18.20,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,120)}I watched the millions of stars as they disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:24.71,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,And waved them goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:29.79,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1400)}So happy for them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:37.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:40.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me try out my new move on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I call it "Toughen up in 120 hours"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:45.91,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, here we go, let's dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:45.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, whoops, let's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:50.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.  My new move!  My new mooove!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:52.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like "BAM"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:55.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they cute, Shiina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:57.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, is this an elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:06.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, fine!  I'll go ask Ooyama-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:07.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We keep getting more and more brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:11.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.  Are you talking to {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.30,0:02:12.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:15.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  You're still saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After bawling in Otonashi's arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:20.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd you say was crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:25.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, realize the greatness of clothespins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:29.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Realize how worthless you are in comparison to clothespins...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:37.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Clothespins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:38.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They can hold stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They can hold it and it won't fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:41.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your clean clothes won't get dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:46.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!  They can even be used as replacements for paperclips!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:49.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In comparison to that, what am {\i1}I{\i0} ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:51.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good for anything at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:53.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use hypnotism for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-san!  Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer to conduct myself peacefully as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:02.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's peaceful about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:06.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The man's kneeling and crying his eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:08.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-kun, Naoi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:10.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got some business to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in here please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:16.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling us into a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:22.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoi-kun, I want you to try and recover Otonashi-kun's lost memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:24.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you giving me an order?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:26.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's your leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:31.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do what she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:31.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  Your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoi-kun's hypnotism is the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:41.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be able to get back your lost memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd certainly like to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go deciding that on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not telling me you'd rather stay like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:55.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to remember again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:58.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... what's this anxious feeling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:02.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it... because if I get them back...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:05.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this daily life might not be able to continue?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:07.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:09.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have I really...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}grown to love living with these guys that much?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, if I remember my past...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:19.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will I still be able to continue like normal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still... even so{|fscx300}-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:21.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,50)}Otonashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:26.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what your past is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,please don't lose sight of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:38.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:41.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your ally too, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:42.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, it helps to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:44.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  What's with that difference?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just sit down, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, is school fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm not even attending.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:11.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go, it might be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:14.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be fun if my head worked better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty dumb...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:19.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no place for people with bad grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't studying fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:23.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:26.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your friends?  Do you play with friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:30.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching TV or playing games alone is more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:33.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing along with your friends' hobbies...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:36.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,laughing at their jokes even when they're not funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,all that does is tire me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:41.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  I'm looking forward to studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to making friends, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:46.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:03.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... don't know why I'm alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no reason to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no interest in others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Living without concern for others...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:10.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the way to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:15.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Working a job that earns me just enough to eat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A life like that was enough...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But even so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I always continued to visit my younger sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With my meager income...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd buy her manga magazines.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd always just go into the bookstore...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and arbitrarily grab something off the counter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, I didn't even know if it was the same magazine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:38.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's possible it was a different magazine...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and she wasn't able to follow the stories properly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:43.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:47.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My sister always loved it and said the same thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:50.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, it seemed she'd be happy with anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My sister was different than me..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:55.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She had hope in her life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:58.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Surely, she'd be able to find a reason to live as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:06:59.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:01.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for two straight years...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}her life was spent confined to a hospital bed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was pitiable...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wished I could trade places with her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I, with no hope...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}no reason to live... if we could switch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those feelings of compassion...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:16.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kept bringing me back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:19.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Winter came.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summer was bad enough...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:24.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but my job in Winter was that much worse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My fingertips would grow numb...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:27.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and feel like they were ready to fall off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:30.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I continued on in order to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:32.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To live...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:36.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shouldn't think about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:40.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I think about it, I'll probably just quit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to at least keep doing this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to eat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:46.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and to buy presents for my younger sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:51.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:54.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For Christmas, I'll talk to the doctor...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and maybe she can go outside for a little while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:08:00.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if you can still use a wheelchair when the snow is packed up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:03.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, if not, I'll just carry her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:06.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be able to handle carrying her with no problem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, we'll go to her favorite shop and buy her whatever she wants.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:13.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can manage it, I'd like to take her to a nice shop to have some cake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd better start saving.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:21.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can get out for Christmas, where would you like to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To Main Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:28.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well cause, all the trees, they have lights on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:29.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:32.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I don't really go there on Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it's really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was last year, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:38.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the doctor said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then shall we go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:43.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:45.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to negotiate so you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they say no... I'll take you out in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:48.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:52.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!  Thank you, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:57.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the biggest thank you I've ever gotten.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:01.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:05.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I started working multiple jobs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:08.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I did at home was sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that I've got a goal, I feel like I can really work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My only worry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:18.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was that her condition seemed to be worsening.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not surprisingly, I didn't get permission to let her leave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:25.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waited until after visiting hours were over...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}snuck into her room...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:31.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and took her out into the night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:38.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!  Hey, can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:42.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.  It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:43.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:45.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:47.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I saw it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:48.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:53.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's have even more fun, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First up is your present!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:10:01.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a matter of fact, your dear brother saved up a ton of cash for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So even if it's expensive, I'll get you whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:04.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go into a shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a jewelry store would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we just go to a department store?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:13.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:22.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After shopping, there's plenty more waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:24.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:29.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know about this stuff, but I got a reservation for a good-looking place from a magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:31.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They serve you in courses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A full-course dinner!  Amazing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:35.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be my first time trying it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:41.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1100)}{\i1}After that, I kept talking alone, and walked on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really live there all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you be lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:50.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:53.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  Will you really be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:55.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you run into any trouble, let me know right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:58.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can come to eat over here any time you want, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:01.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:04.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything you've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:11.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}had a reason to live the whole time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:15.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That reason was... right next to me all along.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:17.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just didn't realize it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:21.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To hear her say, "thank you"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just by hearing that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was able to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just by feeling loved by her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was able to feel alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:35.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm such a fool.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:37.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To only realize that now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was such a precious existence...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:41.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I didn't do anything for her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:44.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was always...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in the hospital...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:48.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}{\i1}with nothing to do but read the manga magazines I brought her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With only that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With a life like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was she truly happy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My life after losing her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it over as well?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The days I spent satisfied with a happiness I never noticed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}those times had passed away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:11.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:15.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing left at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:36.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I can find a reason to live again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:39.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A reason to live... I think I can find it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can devote my life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:45.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the sake of someone else...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:19.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you remembered?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:20.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:24.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like you're about to say it was a great life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:26.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I need to be alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:42.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had a shallow and colorless existence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:46.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until you taught me that there was a reason to live...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I found it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I died halfway through my dream?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Died without finishing anything?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That can't be it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:58.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can't...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't even die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:03.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatsune!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:15.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you calmed down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:20.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural to feel a little upset after your memories return.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty weak, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've realized how strong you are all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:36.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, has anything changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:37.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:40.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like your feelings... are you going to continue to fight in the warfront?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:43.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:44.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't die like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:48.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you've found a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:49.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:51.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, I'm in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:03.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you said you had a report?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough meal tickets for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do?  Should we go for Tornado?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:09.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:13.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's operation is... Monster Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:17.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:19.02,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,A carnival of despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:23.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean monsters exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:24.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  The King of the River.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:28.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,King of the River?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A little ways from here, there's a river, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go top off our food provisions there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:38.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait... is this just simple river-fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:41.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... why, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:45.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got taken in by the name and imagined something ridiculous again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:49.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who'll win?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:51.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to this~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:52.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:09.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm weeding, among other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:20.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all gonna go river-fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:21.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,River?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's against the rules to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:25.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the Student Council President anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:30.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the rules for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still a student...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you bring her with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:49.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's let her join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:50.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy of the Warfront!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:57.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.  She's not our enemy anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:59.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah but she's still {\i1}kinda{\i0} the Student Council President!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:03.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, we also have the current replacement President.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:06.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, I'm God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:15.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not the Student Council President anymore.  It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:19.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you feeling alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:21.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're getting an incredible member...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:24.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... how come you guys don't have any gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:27.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We already contacted the Guild, so we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:30.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got an appropriate maniac in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:31.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maniac?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:38.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His name's Saitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:41.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's knowledgable about guns...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:45.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the Guild, he's known as Fish Saitou.  He's a fishing maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:51.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He brought all those fishing supplies in a cart for this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How much does this guy love fishing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another idiot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:58.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.  Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:10.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:21.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have been your ally in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was never a person like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't it be alright if there was?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:28.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Even if there were, they'd just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's okay to make friends with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's all fish together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:46.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:47.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong.  That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:52.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First you pick a lure, and hook some bait or a worm onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:57.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any problems with bugs, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:58.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for the river and cast with all your might.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:10.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takeyamaaaaaa~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:14.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Chriiiiiiiist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:16.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some superhuman strength, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:19.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Overdrive is passive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:20.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Passive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:21.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:25.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... with you, it could be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What could?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:29.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Catching the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:33.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the name of the operation, that thing's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:38.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's pulling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Monster Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:50.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:54.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We usually see Monster Stream as a sign of the King's anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:56.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, we evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:57.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl just might be able to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:05.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How big is the thing?  The rod will break!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate my craftsmanship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:10.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was made to handle even the King of the River!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:13.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it's impossible at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, you guys are going for the King?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:17.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way that'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:17.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita-godan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:20.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you some meat udon.  Come and help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:21.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:25.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oho, Hinata-senpai.  You're looking awfully unguarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!  How about I kick you as hard as I can and send you flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:31.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop thinking up stupid stuff and help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We need reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:34.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:35.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:42.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you lot!  Pull harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:50.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Heave-ho!  Heave-ho!  Heave-ho!  Heave-ho!  Heave-ho!  Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:48.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:57.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She pulled it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one's the monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:00.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:02.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:04.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fall, we'll get eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.03,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Crazy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God never falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:09.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna get eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:14.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:29.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... with all this, we won't need to use Tornado for a while, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:30.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean we'll eat this every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:33.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we worry about that, worry about how we'll even preserve it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:36.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it seems a waste to throw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:37.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we've no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:40.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make it into one big meal, and treat the regular students.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:42.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:43.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:51.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just like charity work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:54.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a warfront... we're acting more like a ministry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:57.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we don't really have an enemy to fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:59.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we going to stop being a warfront anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:01.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, what in the world will we be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:06.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Slacking So We Don't Vanish Team"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:07.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:09.96,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fn\fs40}Chop, chop, chop, chop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:14.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never thought a time like this would come.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.18,0:22:20.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tachibana.  May I call you by your first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.88,0:22:22.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:23.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're closer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:24.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:26.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:29.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishing together... cooking together...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:31.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and besides... when I first heard it, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:34.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.01,0:22:36.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:37.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I like your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:40.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade means, "to play a song", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:43.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's how you'd like to interpret it, I'm okay with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:47.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Yuzuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:49.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written like "to tie a string".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:48.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TL Note: This can mean bowstring or a string on an instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:50.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like it if you call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:54.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:55.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got something I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:56.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:23:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please stay with us from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:01.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:04.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to fight anybody anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.99,0:23:06.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay with us and have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.68,0:23:11.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And... because...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:14.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just like being with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:15.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:18.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want, it's what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.61,0:23:22.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:23.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:30.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.81,0:23:32.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I haven't seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:35.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably off observing somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:39.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not really the kind to participate in charity like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:41.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you help out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:45.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.50,0:23:49.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe!  Who did this to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:51.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.75,0:23:52.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:58.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!  Kanade was with me the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:10.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:18.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c201] Matsushita-Godan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.52,0:24:19.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c186] In other words, we're trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.29,0:24:20.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c73] I pray that we may meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.25,0:24:20.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c183] A trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.47,0:24:22.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c110] I can't distract someone that scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:20.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c145] What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.29,0:24:22.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c52] Let me give you a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.90,0:24:22.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c36] Is Kanade okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.46,0:24:22.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c82] Angel Player...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.01,0:24:24.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c283] Let me explain and cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.38,0:24:23.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c233] How fooliiiish!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.80,0:24:24.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c228] It seems the time has come to show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.55,0:24:25.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c161] I'll leave behind the things that didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.15,0:24:25.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c151] Sure looks busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.10,0:24:26.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c326] Please be safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.41,0:24:27.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c327] Kanade!
