Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:23:04.17,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}They'll continue to live only through their memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:11.84,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}Rather than try to love and laugh at this loneliness
